292
00:19:10,160 --> 00:19:11,160
I see.

293
00:19:16,350 --> 00:19:19,230
Where do you live in Wugui Sea?
(Watch on www.kisskh.ws to support Admin)

294
00:19:22,160 --> 00:19:23,160
Over there.

295
