Why exactly did you come here?

302
00:19:48,070 --> 00:19:49,420
Is it to kill Ji Bozai?

303
00:19:50,550 --> 00:19:52,310
I also think he doesn't
deserve to beat you.

304
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:54,660
You're not wrong about that.

305
00:19:56,400 --> 00:19:58,246
I mean I'm not that person,

306
00:19:58,270 --> 00:20:00,006
but what you said is right.

307
00:20:00,030 --> 00:20:01,030
Ming Yi.

308
00:20:04,240 --> 00:20:05,620
Are you having a good life here?

309
00:20:10,160 --> 00:20:12,726
Judgment Hall doesn't
need to care about that.

310
00:20:12,750 --> 00:20:14,550
I'm not asking as someone
from Judgment Hall.

311
00:20:15,510 --> 00:20:17,180
You must have gone through a lot

312
00:20:17,310 --> 00:20:18,310
that you can't tell me.

313
00:20:20,240 --> 00:20:21,810
I just want to know one thing.

314
00:20:28,640 --> 00:20:29,640
Are you

315
00:20:30,960 --> 00:20:31,980
doing well?

316
00:20:47,440 --> 00:20:48,880
Lord Hanfeng has given orders today.

317
00:20:49,070 --> 00:20:50,070
I must come.

318
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:52,000
Only in this way

319
00:20:52,160 --> 00:20:53,490
can you stay out of trouble.

320
00:20:58,240 --> 00:20:59,770
What's this?

321
00:21:00,960 --> 00:21:03,010
An artifact specially made by Lord Hanfeng.

322
00:21:03,550 --> 00:21:04,550
It's said

323
00:21:04,640 --> 00:21:07,380
to be able to detect the aura
of netherbeasts precisely.

324
00:21:20,590 --> 00:21:22,700
That's the direction of Spirit Well.

325
00:21:22,920 --> 00:21:23,980
We can't let them find it.

326
00:21:24,240 --> 00:21:26,526
Isn't that Immortal Ji's treasury?

327
00:21:26,550 --> 00:21:27,550
Treasury?

328
00:21:28,030 --> 00:21:29,030
Over there.

329
00:21:35,270 --> 00:21:37,530
How could there be
netherbeasts in Wugui Sea?

330
00:21:38,200 --> 00:21:39,526
Mu Qibai must be using

331
00:21:39,550 --> 00:21:42,310
the search for netherbeasts as an
excuse to find Golden Millet Dream.

332
00:21:42,680 --> 00:21:44,660
We must find a way to drive them off.

333
00:21:45,960 --> 00:21:47,570
The treasury holds.

334
00:21:47,750 --> 00:21:50,176
Immortal Ji's most precious artifacts.

335
00:21:50,200 --> 00:21:51,936
They must be kept from fire and light.

336
00:21:51,960 --> 00:21:53,046
If anything happens,

337
00:21:53,070 --> 00:21:54,570
