730
00:42:53,360 --> 00:42:54,640
It seems you really are friends.

731
00:42:56,360 --> 00:42:59,080
Your Lordship, why are you
accompanying Ming Yi to Moonlit Blossoms?

732
00:42:59,110 --> 00:43:01,150
Zhang Tai is marrying
someone from Yousu Fox Tribe.

733
00:43:01,550 --> 00:43:03,086
In the whole divine
capital of Jixing Abyss,

734
00:43:03,110 --> 00:43:04,430
