735
00:43:08,230 --> 00:43:09,230
Xun Ming?

736
00:43:12,440 --> 00:43:13,650
Mu Qibai and the others

737
00:43:14,070 --> 00:43:16,510
have always worried the Sunken
Abyss affair would be exposed.

738
00:43:17,110 --> 00:43:19,780
Ming Yi's parents died from
Blood Pearl Bloom poison.

739
00:43:20,550 --> 00:43:22,420
And she exposed it
publicly to seek justice.

740
00:43:24,760 --> 00:43:25,760
Clearly,

741
00:43:26,440 --> 00:43:27,900
Ming Yi isn't on their side.

742
00:43:28,670 --> 00:43:30,900
That makes her even safer and more useful.

743
00:43:32,670 --> 00:43:35,050
If Zhang Tai really is marrying Xun Ming,

744
00:43:35,840 --> 00:43:36,856
