748
00:43:44,440 --> 00:43:46,090
It seems I've overlooked.

749
00:43:47,000 --> 00:43:48,320
It turns out these past few days,

750
00:43:48,400 --> 00:43:49,936
you've nearly given away
all of Wugui Sea's wealth

751
00:43:49,960 --> 00:43:50,960
